<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Project2</title>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag    'application', media: 'all', 'data-turbolinks-track' => true %>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag params[:controller], 'data-turbolinks-track' => true %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag 'application', 'data-turbolinks-track' => true %>
  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag "https://fonts.googleapis.com/icon?family=Material+Icons" %>
</head>
<body>

<!-- The drawer is always open in large screens. The header is always shown,
  even in small screens. -->
<div class="mdl-layout mdl-js-layout mdl-layout--fixed-drawer mdl-layout--fixed-header">
  <header class="mdl-layout__header">
    <div class="mdl-layout__header-row">
      <div class="mdl-layout-spacer">
      </div>
      <div class="mdl-textfield mdl-js-textfield mdl-textfield--expandable mdl-textfield--floating-label mdl-textfield--align-right">

  




      	<%=link_to "Ocean", users_path, class:"btn btn-primary" %>
        <%=link_to "Cove", users_path, class:"btn btn-primary" %>
      	<button id="demo-menu-lower-right" class="btn btn-primary">Pools<i class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-down"></i></button>



		<ul class="mdl-menu mdl-menu--bottom-right mdl-js-menu mdl-js-ripple-effect"
		    for="demo-menu-lower-right">
		  <li class="mdl-menu__item">Some Action</li>
		  <li class="mdl-menu__item">Another Action</li>
		  <li class="mdl-menu__item">Yet Another Actiony Action</li>
		  <!-- WILL DYNAMICALLY PULL POOL NAMES TO POPULATE -->
		</ul>

        <label class="mdl-button mdl-js-button mdl-button--icon" for="fixed-header-drawer-exp">
          <i class="material-icons">search</i>
        </label>
        <div class="mdl-textfield__expandable-holder">
          <input class="mdl-textfield__input" type="text" name="sample" id="fixed-header-drawer-exp">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>


  <div class="mdl-layout__drawer">
    <div class="col-sm-12">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-sm-12">
            <div class="image-cropper">
                <img src="http://www.cbc.ca/strombo/content/images/Morgan-Freeman-The-Hour.jpg" class="rounded" />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <br>

        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-sm-12 left-navigation">
            <h5>Morgan Freeman and Chevy Chase</h5>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-sm-12 left-navigation">
            <p>Diamond Heights</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-sm-12 left-navigation">
            <h6><b>Parenting Mission</b></h6>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-sm-12 left-navigation">
            <p>As parents, we are interested in creating habits of thought, reading, writing, and speaking which go beneath surface meaning, first impressions, dominant myths, official pronouncements, traditional clich√©s, received wisdom, and mere opinions, to understand the deep meaning, root causes, social context, ideology, and personal consequences of any action, event, object, process, organization, experience, text, subject matter, policy, mass media, or discourse.</p>
          </div>
        </div>


        <nav class="mdl-navigation">
          <a class="mdl-navigation__link" href="">Link</a>
          <a class="mdl-navigation__link" href="">Link</a>
          <a class="mdl-navigation__link" href="">Link</a>
          <a class="mdl-navigation__link" href="">Link</a>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <main class="mdl-layout__content">
    <div class="page-content">
	    <%= yield %>
	    <p><%= "End of Page" %></p><!-- ONLY HERE FOR TESTING -->
	</div>
  </main>


</div>



</body>
<style>

.image-cropper {
    width: 180px;
    height: 180px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: 50%;
}

.left-navigation {
  width:215px;
  margin-top: 0px;
  margin-bottom: 0px;
}

img {
    display: inline;
    margin: 0 auto;
    height: 100%;
    width: auto;
}

.page-content {
	padding-left: 30px;
}
.glyphicon {
	padding-left: 10px;
}
</style>
</html>
